author: Luke Hammill | The Oregonian/OregonLive
title: MAX lines delayed 15 minutes due to mechanical issue
text:
All MAX lines are delayed by 15 minutes through 5 p.m. Friday, TriMet announced.
The delay is due to a mechanical issue in downtown Portland.
